{
  "script_function_map": [
    {
      "line_group_id": "LG01",
      "timeline_start": "00:00",
      "timeline_end": "00:03",
      "script_text": "别再让 AI 给你定 KPI 了。",
      "script_function": "hook / conflict_label",
      "data_goal_service": "primary_variable: opening_route_or_first_5s_packaging"
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "LG02",
      "timeline_start": "00:03",
      "timeline_end": "00:08",
      "script_text": "它写“播放多少、点赞多少、客资多少”，看着很完整，但大多数时候没用。",
      "script_function": "pain_point_expand",
      "data_goal_service": "opening_route_or_first_5s_packaging + evidence_compression"
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "LG03",
      "timeline_start": "00:08",
      "timeline_end": "00:14",
      "script_text": "因为这些数字不会告诉你：下一条到底改标题、改开头，还是改中段结构。",
      "script_function": "core_problem_definition",
      "data_goal_service": "opening_route_or_first_5s_packaging"
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "LG04",
      "timeline_start": "00:14",
      "timeline_end": "00:20",
      "script_text": "我一开始也这样问：帮视频工厂定个目标，最好有播放、点赞、客资。",
      "script_function": "human_process_anchor",
      "data_goal_service": "evidence_compression"
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "LG05",
      "timeline_start": "00:20",
      "timeline_end": "00:27",
      "script_text": "第一版确实很全，北极星目标、阶段目标、指标树、客资定义都有。但我看完觉得不对。",
      "script_function": "ordinary_ai_output_then_rejection",
      "data_goal_service": "result_diff_display"
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "LG06",
      "timeline_start": "00:27",
      "timeline_end": "00:33",
      "script_text": "它还是在回答：我要追哪些数字。我真正需要的是：数据回来以后，下一轮该改哪里。",
      "script_function": "reversal_point",
      "data_goal_service": "opening_route_or_first_5s_packaging + result_diff_display"
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "LG07",
      "timeline_start": "00:33",
      "timeline_end": "00:41",
      "script_text": "所以我又追问：让 AI 设计一套目标驱动的数据飞轮。每期发布后，根据播放、留存、收藏、评论、私信、客资，判断下一期只改哪个变量。",
      "script_function": "structured_prompt_process",
      "data_goal_service": "evidence_compression + result_diff_display"
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "LG08",
      "timeline_start": "00:41",
      "timeline_end": "00:47",
      "script_text": "这次结果才像个判断系统。",
      "script_function": "result_turn",
      "data_goal_service": "result_diff_display"
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "LG09",
      "timeline_start": "00:47",
      "timeline_end": "00:54",
      "script_text": "播放和留存，是触达。点赞和收藏，是认可。评论和追问，是互动。",
      "script_function": "evidence_explanation_metric_layers",
      "data_goal_service": "evidence_compression"
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "LG10",
      "timeline_start": "00:54",
      "timeline_end": "01:01",
      "script_text": "私信也不能全算客资，要看他是不是说清楚任务、场景和结果。",
      "script_function": "lead_quality_boundary",
      "data_goal_service": "evidence_compression"
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "LG11",
      "timeline_start": "01:01",
      "timeline_end": "01:06",
      "script_text": "所以目标不是 KPI 表。",
      "script_function": "judgment_card_turn",
      "data_goal_service": "opening_route_or_first_5s_packaging + result_diff_display"
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "LG12",
      "timeline_start": "01:06",
      "timeline_end": "01:12",
      "script_text": "真正有用的目标，是逼你回答三件事：哪一层出了问题，下一条只改哪个变量，改完看哪个指标。",
      "script_function": "core_framework_summary",
      "data_goal_service": "opening_route_or_first_5s_packaging + evidence_compression"
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "LG13",
      "timeline_start": "01:12",
      "timeline_end": "01:16",
      "script_text": "没有这套判断，你每轮都在动，却不知道哪一步起作用。",
      "script_function": "risk_if_no_system",
      "data_goal_service": "opening_route_or_first_5s_packaging"
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "LG14",
      "timeline_start": "01:16",
      "timeline_end": "01:22",
      "script_text": "播放是入口。收藏是认可。私信要评分。每条只改一个主变量。目标清楚了，动作才不会乱；复盘清楚了，下一步才会浮出来。",
      "script_function": "summary_card_and_closing",
      "data_goal_service": "primary_variable: opening_route_or_first_5s_packaging, supporting: evidence_compression/result_diff_display"
    }
  ],
